1039
01:22:13,942 --> 01:22:14,982
So how did you get here?

1040
01:22:15,192 --> 01:22:17,523
- Boo Ali brought us here.
- Boo Ali.

1041
01:22:17,525 --> 01:22:18,691
Boo Ali is an agent.

1042
01:22:18,692 --> 01:22:20,898
