I will definitely shoot you.

1086
01:25:29,400 --> 01:25:30,232
Come on.

1087
01:25:33,317 --> 01:25:36,023
- And find out who the hell is Boo Ali?
- Yes, sir.

1088
01:26:05,942 --> 01:26:07,023
Hail Sri Ram.

1089
01:26:07,025 --> 01:26:09,523
Sir, he's definitely crazy.

1090
