Bali's devotee, then do come back.

1109
01:27:21,567 --> 01:27:23,107
It's a promise, sir.

1110
01:27:28,692 --> 01:27:31,523
Hail Sri Ram!

1111
01:27:40,567 --> 01:27:41,732
You're right.

1112
01:27:42,775 --> 01:27:44,523
He's definitely crazy.

1113
