1116
01:28:00,025 --> 01:28:07,607
<i>♪ I am your voice... you're my words. ♪</i>

1117
01:28:07,775 --> 01:28:14,148
<i>♪ I heard what you never said. ♪</i>

1118
01:28:14,567 --> 01:28:21,357
<i>♪ Since we met... I feel capable. ♪</i>

1119
01:28:22,150 --> 01:28:28,773
<i>♪ Since we met...
